At BNY Mellon, we are at the' forefront of digitally transforming the financial services industry. The API Platform supports hundreds of internal and external APIs, with dozens of strategic financial services clients depending on our stability and success. We support the API lifecycle, from publishing to consumption to support. The API Platform team is distributed across Jersey City and in the U.S., and Chennai and Pune in India. We are expected to build and operate a 24/7 platform.

Role

As an API Platform DevOps Engineer, you will be part of the team that builds, maintains, and promotes our API Platform and related services. We build and operate the infrastructure that powers BNY Mellon's API infrastructure, publishing tools, and API mediation/orchestration services. You will be responsible for implementing, monitoring and scaling our internal containerized/cloud-based infrastructure, while ensuring best practices for build and deployment.

We combine the open source WSO2 product with in-house built services to deliver an end-to-end API Platform.

